{"tid":1679214,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"麥浚龍嘅畫眉三部曲 高汁過曬所有新歌","createTime":"2019-10-28T05:30:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T15:51:01.000Z","uid":218219,"like":18,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bde960f3efcaaa7d63fed231abd5c90faaf494f9","tid":1679214,"uid":218219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:30:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hOgBeOUEwWs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhOgBeOUEwWs&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD53GrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=506639aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hOgBeOUEwWs</a><br />\n<br />\n時候有點早 你竟因我悠然飛到<br />\n怎愛你未必知道<br />\n誰是你或者想知道<br />\n<br />\n黃泥下只得我跟你<br />\n紅塵內建造紀念碑<br />\n圍城外得到最親的距離<br />\n當魔鬼都想幫我忘懷全人類<br />\n好好呵護你<br />\n在閻羅地府你是我的 別要死<br />\n像受了傷的一隻畫眉<br />\n在沒有星的一塊園地 愛你<br />\n<br />\n然後幾多擁抱過後抱住有幾多<br />\n陪畫眉沉睡過 而甦醒很清楚<br />\n而分開不必講 道歉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aeb8d4e74d5775b6033ad18c9a64c6d13828727","tid":1679214,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:31:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zyBfyPB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzyBfyPB.jpg&h=2708f4ca&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"71fb71e4bc65c371237f59a242ce33cf23afb524","tid":1679214,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:35:39.000Z","msg":"便繼續繼續想知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e580764b9731a6e15899d153d91a33c74be4f223","tid":1679214,"uid":43737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:38:35.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"48831be698d32f2e50ff0008134b56379cd1e221","tid":1679214,"uid":156751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5978bbe0018703f04c98f040b5b2ac6e4b9a26","tid":